Packages 
Package Description
backend
Contains the behind the scenes classes utilized by PEMS.
backend.exceptions
Contains classes for all custom exceptions thrown by PEMS.
backend.peripheral
Package used to store classes pertaining to the detection and importation of evidence files from external hardware.
backend.storage
Set of classes used to represent the structure of the /cases/ directory managed by PEMS.
backend.storage.file
Includes classes used to represent the evidence files managed by PEMS.
backend.storage.file.img
Consists of only one eponymous class: Img.
gui
Package used to store all classes related to the PEMS graphical user interface.
gui.components
Comprehensive package encompassing all graphics components designed specifically for use within the PEMS GUI.
gui.components.field
Package containing custom instances of JTextField used by PEMS.
gui.components.icon
Package containing the class for the ImgIcon component, as well as its subclasses.
gui.display
Package used to store the code for the various subclasses of JPanel that comprise the PEMS GUI.
gui.display.dialogues
Package containing classes for the various custom GUI dialogues displayed by PEMS.
gui.display.editcase
Contains EditCasePanel, the screen displayed when a user opts to edit a previously existing case.
gui.display.editimg
Contains classes for the image editing user interface.
gui.display.finish
Contains FinishPanel, the screen displayed when the user finishes editing a given case.
gui.display.newcase
Contains NewCasePanel, the screen displayed when a user opts to create a new case from scratch.
gui.display.select
Contains SelectPanel, the primary user interface for evidence file importation.
gui.display.start
Contains StartPanel, the initial screen displayed upon running PEMS.
gui.window
Package containing the custom instances of JFrame used by PEMS.
runtime
Package utilized at program runtime to initialize the GUI.
